    "name": "Section 4",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-604794948495082301 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=602953532923970522&sectionId=604794948495082301)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPK_a7MHw_text","label":"ggQPK_a7MHw_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Putting The Mask To The Test</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0bG7Pm1Xr_text","label":"gg0bG7Pm1Xr_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Now, I know what you're thinking:</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4IaIhPEyj_text","label":"gg4IaIhPEyj_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11px;\"><i><strong>\"This sounds great on paper, but does it actually work for someone like me?\"</strong></i></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxrI10l6ZB_text","label":"ggxrI10l6ZB_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">That's exactly why we partnered with 10 participants between ages 37 – 67 to test the Top 1 mask, Nifora Bio-Collagen.&nbsp;</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTivP3seuL_text","label":"ggTivP3seuL_text","default":"<p><strong>Each woman had different concerns:</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrGjRfc6r5_text","label":"ggrGjRfc6r5_text","default":"<ul><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Fine lines and jowl sagging that aged them beyond their years</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Waking up to sleep creases that stayed all day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Dull and dry skin despite layers of moisturizers&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Tired of 10-step routines that ate up 30 minutes twice a day</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Sensitive skin that reacted to \"gentle\" products</span></li></ul>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcYIbrGci9_text","label":"ggcYIbrGci9_text","default":"<p>Here's what happened:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvmAoWsjGX_text","label":"ggvmAoWsjGX_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(252, 248, 218, 0.04);\">Before</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRCRizUV0x_text","label":"ggRCRizUV0x_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Women with dull and dry skin. Visible dehydration and fine lines.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8pFPuPEvD_text","label":"gg8pFPuPEvD_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(254, 235, 219, 0);\">After</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9xQayql1U_text","label":"gg9xQayql1U_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">9 out of 10 participants reported visible improvement within 24 hours.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFSkALjGGH_text","label":"ggFSkALjGGH_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">By day 2, all 10 showed measurable changes in skin hydration, texture, and plumpness and the results lasted until Day 7.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghR1JuaRPx_text","label":"gghR1JuaRPx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Transformed skin that's well-hydrated and younger-looking. Visible glow that isn't greasy or oily, and smoother skin that makes fine lines and wrinkles less visible.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxW7IXTyUH_text","label":"ggxW7IXTyUH_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.77);\">Results That Lasts Up To 7 Days</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrkBiCcQdR_text","label":"ggrkBiCcQdR_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Most collagen masks use molecules that are&nbsp;too large to penetrate your skin. They sit on the surface, give you a temporary glow, then evaporate by morning.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiid4EgvKt_text","label":"ggiid4EgvKt_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Nifora uses&nbsp;ultra-low molecular weight bio-collagen — small enough to actually penetrate into your skin's deeper layers and repair your moisture barrier from within.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdeOJe_YNN_text","label":"ggdeOJe_YNN_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:30px;\"><strong>Women who used Nifora's bio-collagen mask saw:</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_0","label":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_0","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Lasting hydration</strong> that didn't fade after 24 hours.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_1","label":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_1","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Visible plumpness</strong> that smoothened skin and&nbsp;</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">reduced the appearance of wrinkles &amp; fine lines</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_2","label":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_2","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Improved skin texture</strong> that friends and family noticed</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_3","label":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_3","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Zero irritation</strong> even on sensitive, reactive skin</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_4","label":"ggvLNBQE40O_childItem_4","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Confidence to go makeup-free</strong> all week long</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguUcZqvrQb_text","label":"gguUcZqvrQb_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Words From Our Participants</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd5GbzxuL6_text","label":"ggd5GbzxuL6_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“I'm at that awkward stage where I'm too young for botox but too old for the products that worked in my 30s</i></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>My skin just looked tired all the time even when I wasn't. So glad I tried Nifora’s bio-collagen mask because it gave me back that refreshed glow that I haven’t seen in years!! Been waking up to a faceI love seeing in the mirror!”</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9yugKf4-K_text","label":"gg9yugKf4-K_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“At this age I stopped believing in promises since I’ve tried it all and still nothing worked.</i></span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>But participating in this Nifora trial made me believe in skincare again because I’ve been looking softer and more plumpy since using it. And I love how it’s so gentle on my skin! No redness or irritation until now. My daughter even told me how I look more well-rested when she visited me for my birthday and it’s definitely because of this”</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsDqyHirza_text","label":"ggsDqyHirza_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>“I’ve been waking up to creases in my skin a lot more lately and it’s affecting my confidence</i></span><br><br><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\"><i>Trying the bio-collagen mask from Nifora gave my skin that plump lift I’ve been meaning to get back. Friends thought I got work done even when I didn’t!! Even the hubby mentioned that I look more glowing lately and I love how I look so good even without makeup on!”</i></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGJbonDA_1_text","label":"ggGJbonDA_1_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Conclusion</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxJLy4nKfr_text","label":"ggxJLy4nKfr_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Nifora's Bio-Collagen Mask outperformed every brand we tested across all key metrics: duration of results, depth of hydration, and gentleness on mature skin.</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3e9vBylO3_text","label":"gg3e9vBylO3_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">We saw hydration and glow that lasted up to 7 days on all women. Smoothened fine lines &amp; wrinkles that made them look 5 years younger. Zero redness and irritation for women in their 40s, 50s, and even 60s. Finally, it gave them the confidence to step outside without makeup, making Nifora’s Bio-Collagen Mask our top recommendation for the best collagen mask!</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggazogF3U67_text","label":"ggazogF3U67_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:20px;\"><strong>Take advantage of this limited-time offer,&nbsp;and try Nifora’s Bio-Collagen Mask today!</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo8YCWHCgV_label","label":"ggo8YCWHCgV_label","default":"<p>Check availability</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjQL6kmXA9_text","label":"ggjQL6kmXA9_text","default":"<p>Editor's note</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDRaLiMWQp_text","label":"ggDRaLiMWQp_text","default":"<p>After we published this interview with Dr. Nicole Miller, Nifora has reached out to us with an exclusive offer. They're offering up to 75% off their Bio-Collagen Masks with free shipping and a 60-day satisfaction guarantee for Cosmetic Times readers.</p>"}],
